headline: What to watch out for in your 2026 Medicare Advantage plan
summary: Millions of seniors with Medicare Advantage plans can expect slimmed-down benefits, loftier premiums, and a reduced selection of options in 2026 plans.

headline: Managed Care Insurers Trading Down Ahead Of Earnings Season
summary: US managed care insurers were trading down this week ahead of earnings season as the release of Medicare ratings and federal tax credit uncertainty appeared to weigh on stock prices.
